{"tid":500439,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IU摘下K-POP最佳專輯Top20之冠","createTime":"2017-12-15T18:05:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-04T04:58:15.000Z","uid":34643,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"91dbdf0156b5da62ca8d33caaf8d757173351583","tid":500439,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T18:05:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2017/12/20171215-weishin-best-kpop-album-01-600x400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2F20171215-weishin-best-kpop-album-01-600x400.jpg&h=3239dcc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國告示牌（Billboard）今（15）日公布了2017年最佳K-pop專輯Top20榜單，摘下今年「K-pop最佳專輯」冠軍的是IU（李知恩）的《Palette》，而備受注目的BTS防彈少年團《Love Yourself 承 &lsquo;Her&rsquo;》則拿下第3名。<br />\n<br />\n對於本次摘下「K-pop最佳專輯」冠軍的IU，Billboard的評論表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">過去K-POP明星都製作一些膚淺無深度的專輯，而IU的《Palette》卻融合了不同的音樂與故事，並展現了明星華麗之下的真實樣貌，讓聽眾與IU一起展開旅程。評論也談及，IU並不擔心公開那些自我懷疑或憂鬱的時刻，儘管明星在舞台上總是華麗，IU透過音樂告訴人們「明星也是人。」</span><br />\n<br />\nBillboard the 20 Best K-pop Albums of 2017（美國告示牌選出最佳K-POP專輯Top20）：<br />\n1.IU李知恩《Palette調色盤》<br />\n2.Epik High《We&rsquo;ve Done Something Wonderful》<br />\n3.BTS防彈少年團《Love Yourself 承 &lsquo;Her&rsquo;》<br />\n4.白娥娟（白雅言）《Bittersweet》<br />\n5.JJ Project《Verse 2》<br />\n6.Bobby金知元《Love and Fall》<br />\n7.Heize《///》<br />\n8.Highlight《Can You Feel It?》<br />\n9.Suran申秀蘭《Walkin&rsquo;》<br />\n10.Red Velvet《Perfect Velvet》<br />\n11.EXO《The War》<br />\n12.Glen Check《The Glen Check Experience》<br />\n13.B1A4《Rollin&rsquo;》<br />\n14.Zion.T《OO》<br />\n15.太妍《My Voice》<br />\n16.CNBLUE《7 CN》<br />\n17.泰民《Move》<br />\n18.Seventeen《Al1》<br />\n19.TWICE《Twicetagram》<br />\n20.李孝利《Black》"},{"pid":"268d0ef886c565a0243e72a8a0a99b1618d39104","tid":500439,"uid":155902,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T18:07:40.000Z","msg":"正, 有好多album 可以聽...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <i